<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.6">
<l>tuyaril cuṭaroḷi taṉṉuṭaic cōtiniṉ ṟavaṇṇa niṟkavē</l>
<l>tuyariṉ maliyu maṉicar piṟaviyi ṭōṉṟikkaṇ kāṇavantu</l>
<l>tuyaraṅkaḷ ceytutaṉ teyva nilaiyula kilpuka vuykkumammāṉ</l>
<l>ṟuyaramil cīrkaṇṇaṉ māyaṉ pukaḻtuṟṟa yāṉōrtuṉ pamilaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who escaped to enter the world of his divine status after having caused sorrows,</l>
<l>having appeared in the birth of a human who abounds in sorrow, having come for the eye to see,</l>
<l>while he stands the way his sorrowless glowing bright light stands,</l>
<l>sorrowless excellent Kṛṣṇa, the trickster, while he absorbs [my] praise I am without any distress.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
